    <item>
      <title>Version 0.0.1 Alpha</title>
      <link>https://interlinedlist.com</link>
      <sparkle:version>1</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.0.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://interlinedlist.com/release-notes/0.0.1-alpha</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>0.0.1 Alpha</h2>
        <p>First alpha release of InterlinedList for Mac. This build is intended
        for early testers and may contain bugs. Please report issues to the
        InterlinedList team.</p>
        <h3>What's included</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Messages — timeline, compose, reply, repost</li>
          <li>Lists — browser, list detail, rows, schema editor, watchers, connections graph</li>
          <li>Documents — editor with live preview and sync</li>
          <li>Social — profile, roster, follow/unfollow, pending requests</li>
          <li>Notifications — inbox with approve/reject actions</li>
          <li>Settings — account, linked accounts, avatar upload</li>
          <li>Exports — CSV export for messages, lists, list data rows, and follows</li>
          <li>Organizations — member management and role assignment</li>
          <li>Scheduled posts</li>
          <li>Automatic updates via Sparkle</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Known limitations</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Alpha build — expect rough edges</li>
          <li>Some upstream API features are pending server-side availability</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
